  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>Thanks to the unusually light and fine links of this halfling-made +2 chain shirt, it imposes no armor check penalty and the wearer's maximum Dexterity bonus is +5. After a melee attack hits the wearer, he can take a 5-foot step as an immediate action, even if he already took a 5-foot step during his turn. Taking such a step does not interfere with the wearer's movement during his next turn. A suit of mail of sly steps is usually sized for Small creatures.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> +2 chain shirt</p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Magic Arms and Armor, expeditious retreat, creator must be a halfling</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Inner Sea Races",
